Global Drugs of Ursodeoxycholic Acid Market Insights
Drugs of Ursodeoxycholic Acid Market size was valued at USD 1.15 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 1.68 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 5.2% from 2024 to 2030.

Drugs of Ursodeoxycholic Acid Market Overview
The global market for Ursodeoxycholic Acid (UDCA) drugs is expanding due to the growing prevalence of liver diseases, particularly non-alcoholic fatty liver disease (NAFLD) and primary biliary cholangitis (PBC). The market is valued at approximately USD 1.6 billion in 2024 and is expected to grow at a CAGR of 7.5% over the next five years. This growth is driven by an increasing demand for effective therapies, better healthcare infrastructure, and advancements in drug formulations. Additionally, key pharmaceutical companies are focusing on the development of novel UDCA drugs, further accelerating market growth.

